ces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b241eacbbc9c06f61dfc3f03da6e12add03641","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鼻敏感嚴重人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次發作啲人會覺得我好似傷風感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係搭地鐵 附近d人當你有流感咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過，我試過索索聲，比個呀叔小我「有病就戴返口罩啦！」我心諗，你估我想咩！話時話，呢幾日我都好辛苦，幾眼都勁痕，仲有時狂流眼淚... 😢😢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我出街盡量唔索 直接用紙巾貼住個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前成日眼痕就捽 捽到成隻眼紅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf77f5f3e3d50fdeeb2055847aa0c6012ab6cc21","tid":12643,"uid":34721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做左幾次針灸，表示好左8成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我幾年前都做過 但近兩年又復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我喺太子做～<br />\n你之前係針邊度？"},{"pid":"c576f32a6b4c267ad04c178c33527c3a5f6da106","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明啊我而家一去啲空氣唔流通既地方個鼻會塞到完全透唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日聽人講去左外國就冇發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本香港空氣本身就太差 所以先咁多人有鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5def38e28b8cc706cf56dc225b15b7e1ee1087dc","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做左幾次針灸，表示好左8成</blockquote>