/>\n新加坡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都好過香港既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又凍 空氣又差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2b6b17e352a74501b4d274b0aeb2c5dfca112b","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有鼻敏感，呢排冬天反而冇事，夏天就成日一起身就流鼻水流到想死。<br />\n係咪得我一個先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真 上年呢d天氣一訓低就仆街<br />\n今年反而冇事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我年年冬天都瀨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968ec1e5016139a0a9a9e433c9b9c5a1f15c62fc","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓教完全用唔到鼻呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  塞到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打側訓啲鼻水就狂流落黎 真係喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係醒左想訓翻果下先黎鼻敏感 真係屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實訓唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  焗住要起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973d346618e83f73e8cc187f022a6471d3ab9729","tid":12643,"uid":37935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;鼻敏感嚴重人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次發作啲人會覺得我好似傷風感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係搭地鐵 附近d人當你有流感咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我都試過，我試過索索聲，比個呀叔小我「有病就戴返口罩啦！」我心諗，你估我想咩！話時話，呢幾日我都好辛苦，幾眼都勁痕，仲有時狂流眼淚... 😢😢&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n所以我出街盡量唔索 直接用紙巾貼住個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前成日眼痕就捽 捽到成隻眼紅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n眼痕 真係好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n捽又唔得 唔捽又痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一痕就會用熱毛巾敷眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個果時真係成日眼痕，又紅筋，又用熱毛巾敷。係宜家大個左先好返d。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9c4fc2d825900009539d92fc10bbd282da4f6d","tid":12643,"uid":12092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:44:50.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39d6a561b6503e171eaa8a3a4df7dc510a23e81","tid":12643,"uid":27613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"屌原來咁多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名睇醫治良方"},{"pid":"218310530dd8ab0b96c9a9199d463048d01b5f09","tid":12643,"uid":19775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"屌一訓低就塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噴藥又治標不治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有塵蟎正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e29d366795b5ac7f5cddefc633fb072199524e","tid":12643,"uid":26551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:57:09.000Z","msg":"流量多起上黎<br />\n訓住鼻水不斷倒流入食道<br />\n好似飲緊鹽水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7798f455749f7c3bef76dbfd4c35b86863bf634f","tid":12643,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"打算試下天灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天灸好似有限定日子<br />\n每年最凍同最熱個三日先有得做<br />\n今年剩番12月30 31同1月8<br />\n有冇巴絲做過可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac51d9f3ef97881dd9f4a0b45f729992de2b342","tid":12643,"uid":34487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"天氣岩岩轉涼嗰幾日<br />\n可以連續打十個乞痴<br />\n十幾廿秒就係on99企係度係咁打乞痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca9776f415f69e8947b986571cd6fc8cb8a793","tid":12643,"uid":27774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T20:16:25.000Z","msg":"一日可以用成半盒紙巾<br />\n重要呻到個鼻勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a034ac2a24e9a94653c1999fbfedc6130e2ad7ec","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;鼻敏感嚴重人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次發作啲人會覺得我好似傷風感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最慘係搭地鐵 附近d人當你有流感咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n我都試過，我試過索索聲，比個呀叔小我「有病就戴返口罩啦！」我心諗，你估我想咩！話時話，呢幾日我都好辛苦，幾眼都勁痕，仲有時狂流眼淚... 😢😢&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n所以我出街盡量唔索 直接用紙巾貼住個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前成日眼痕就捽 捽到成隻眼紅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n眼痕 真係好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n捽又唔得 唔捽又痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一痕就會用熱毛巾敷眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個果時真係成日眼痕，又紅筋，又用熱毛巾敷。係宜家大個左先好返d。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁 依家反而唔會成日痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一痕會滴埋眼藥水"},{"pid":"56f1d8e1442d5a223ac2079beeeb293b7f855c46","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌一訓低就塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 噴藥又治標不治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有塵蟎正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd49bcbfd136ca351534bee65628af0208e2e5f","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流量多起上黎<br />\n訓住鼻水不斷倒流入食道<br />\n好似飲緊鹽水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鼻塞訓教真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bba6a42e3f2fe993631547822701c3782d9345","tid":12643,"uid":5583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做天灸<br />\n<br />\n利申過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1c3355e5d68cfa5574a4603d2f4fac7bb534bf","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天氣岩岩轉涼嗰幾日<br />\n可以連續打十個乞痴<br />\n十幾廿秒就係on99企係度係咁打乞痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係街打乞痴 啲人當你大白鯊咁走都走唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fd84169ef877be3d4e5702e106ffcc1f931124","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日可以用成半盒紙巾<br />\n重要呻到個鼻勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要整到個鼻損晒又甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83decee9091444f0a558b4192010026b353e0c87","tid":12643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"一起身又打左好多個乞痴先出得門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfa8cb164485ce36e3a1467cf6b28ef858fce27","tid":12643,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而係朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da0245e1f22f6a6aa14175d127a06eb86dc964e","tid":12643,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d384db9c769d63b8a1ba0b6d4a85e2d9655d420e","tid":12643,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而係朝早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一起身狂打"},{"pid":"1c2284373d315f6992da34a337522d4a53fdae51","tid":12643,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b7f003b483c2dbf698c3a93a87d8c939185ec61","tid":12643,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:37:13.000Z","msg":"好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24a3fa5a48bc29ec3239327814a4b7fe66dc8c9","tid":12643,"uid":33179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"臨訓加埋起身就係咁打乞痴 呀媽就係咁話 「傷風就去睇醫生啦！」佢地根本就唔明係鼻敏感發作而唔係傷風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5191cf4c92502e1a06678c97ba1e1a6ecceca32c","tid":12643,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"十二月準備去做天灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b2e65b73914eba3de072e052ab906cda3482d0","tid":12643,"uid":10689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"包住雲呑留名"},{"pid":"a565de8ddfd77fe14dbd4edaad4b77c37c71172c","tid":12643,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一日可以用成半盒紙巾<br />\n重要呻到個鼻勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要整到個鼻損晒又甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce399ef5730aa495c058f5d08db6852e3bc278d","tid":12643,"uid":26067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"可以食收鼻水藥或者敏感藥<br />\n即刻收哂。不過治標不治本。"},{"pid":"0e4a50141fcf7b572470fecd9ebb2c25e8988f74","tid":12643,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有鼻敏感，呢排冬天反而冇事，夏天就成日一起身就流鼻水流到想死。<br />\n係咪得我一個先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我夏天係開左冷氣先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係。唔開又熱 開左第二朝實係咁打乞痴<br />\n<br />\n冬天起身專登吸多d氣個鼻會舒服d"}]}